thread.title: BRIEF-Anhui Anke Biotechnology Group to acquire approval for clinical trial and technique of monoclonal antibody injection

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Anhui Anke Biotechnology Group to acquire approval for clinical trial and technique of monoclonal antibody injection

organizations.name: anhui anke biotechnology group co ltd * says co

text:
Jan 25(Reuters) - Anhui Anke Biotechnology Group Co Ltd
* Says co plans to acquire approval for clinical trial and technique of a kind of monoclonal antibody injection from Jiangsu Aosaikang Pharmaceutical Co Ltd (seller), at the price of 50 million yuan
* Say co also needs to pay sales commissions to seller
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/m4pD9h
